### Monorepo overview and commands

This repository is a pnpm workspace with three packages:

- `durable-execution` – core durable task execution engine
- `durable-execution-storage-drizzle` – Drizzle ORM storage (PostgreSQL, SQLite)
- `durable-execution-orpc-utils` – oRPC utilities to expose/use durable tasks over RPC

Useful references:

- Root README: [README.md](mdc:README.md)
- Core package: [durable-execution/README.md](mdc:durable-execution/README.md)
- Drizzle storage: [durable-execution-storage-drizzle/README.md](mdc:durable-execution-storage-drizzle/README.md)
- oRPC utils: [durable-execution-orpc-utils/README.md](mdc:durable-execution-orpc-utils/README.md)

Top-level scripts (Turbo orchestrated): defined in [package.json](mdc:package.json)

- pnpm build – Build all packages
- pnpm test – Run tests across packages
- pnpm test-coverage – Run tests with coverage
- pnpm type-check – Type-check all packages
- pnpm lint / pnpm lint-fix – Lint all packages
- pnpm fmt / pnpm fmt-check – Format or check formatting
- pnpm clean – Clean build artifacts
- pnpm build-docs – Build TypeDoc docs for core package

Tooling:

- Turbo tasks: [turbo.json](mdc:turbo.json)
- Workspace setup: [pnpm-workspace.yaml](mdc:pnpm-workspace.yaml)
- TypeDoc config: [typedoc.json](mdc:typedoc.json)
